[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ん……ここ、どこ？　\nあれ、私たち……どうして……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "目が覚めたみたいね。大丈夫？　\nどこか痛いところはない？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……状況、把握。ここは敵陣営。\nベスティラでの衝突後、ここに連れ去られたと推測",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうよ。キューンが「そっちに行きたい」って\n言ったから、連れてきたの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "連れてきたって言うには物騒な感じだったけど……\nまあ、そういうことだから、安心しなよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（獣人の国ベスティラで発生していた誘拐事件。\n　その犯人をキューンたちは「管理」すると言った）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（それを止めるべく、私たちは対立した……けど、\n　本当は、キューンは争いなんて望んでいなかった）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（だから、私はキューンを無理矢理こっちに\n　連れ去った。ヤドヴィガは、不服みたいだけど……）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "よろしければ、ご飯をどうぞ。\n温かいうちに召し上がってくださいね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……ご飯？　あ、いい匂い……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "遠慮はいらないさ。仲良くなるには\n食事を共にするのが一番ってもんだろう？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "お腹も空いてるだろうしね。\nまずは食べてから考えなよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……敵の施しを受けるのは、危険。\n……とはいえ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "そうそう。なんかするなら気絶した時にやってるさ。\nだから食べても大丈夫だよ？　多分ね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "やめなさい。あんたが言うと\nシャレに聞こえないんだから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "…………\nじゃあ、ちょっとだけ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ん……美味しい。とっても、優しい味がする……\nほら、ヤド姉も。毒なんてないよ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "あむ……異常なし。\n……いただきます",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "よかったです。おかわりもありますから、\n遠慮せず食べてくださいね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "……その頬当て、外してから食べたらどうだい？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そんなに警戒しなくてもいいのよ。\n私たち、仲間になるんだから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……主の命令が最優先。たとえもてなされても、\n我が主の方針に反するなら、戦う。それが私の役目",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ご馳走を食べても揺るがないとは……冷静なのね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "いやいや、相棒じゃないんだから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "綺麗な宝石とかなら、\n心が揺らぐ可能性もあるんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "そっちはお前さんだけさね。\n大事なのは気持ちだろう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あはは……みんな、仲良しなんだね。\nなんか、こういうの……久しぶりだなぁ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "ふふ……一緒に食べると、心までポカポカしますよね。\nキューンさんが笑顔で、フロッケも嬉しいです",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "うん……ありがとう、フロッケちゃん。\n本当に、温かい……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "キューン……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヤドヴィガ、あんたも本当は、\n自由になりたいって思ってるんじゃない？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……判断、保留。\n私には、まだ分からない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "答えはすぐに出さなくていいさ。\n焦ることはないよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "私、ここにいてもいいのかな……？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "フロッケ",
		"romanized_name": "Flocke",
		"model_path_hash": "8444632684097041943",
		"text": "もちろんです。みんな、\nキューンさんとヤドヴィガさんを歓迎していますよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1324369732733195994",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……うん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "……今は、ここに留まる。\nキューン一人を、置いてはいけない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ふふ、これからよろしくね。二人とも",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "「九偉人」の９番目。控えめな性格で、少し人見知り。\n兄のヘルトについていたが、ヴァレリアに連れ去られた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "「九偉人」の８番目。真面目な性格で、主に忠実。\n兄のヘルトについていたが、ヴァレリアに連れ去られた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "「九偉人」の３番目。いなせな風来坊。\nレスナたちと共に行動している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "「九偉人」の４番目。飄々とした性格。\nレスナたちと共に行動している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]